      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i use insulin for my type 2 and im just looking at my schedule for tonight. i only had like a tiny salad for dinner and barely ate anything compared to usual. is it okay if i just skip my basal dose tonight so my blood sugar doesnt drop too low while i sleep?",
